{"tid":1518871,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"賤命補償基金營運日誌","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:40:30.000Z","uid":125976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e746953e9edacad187cce87dbd81d4e1f658c1","tid":1518871,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"俗語話：「上天閂咗對門，一定會開返對窗。」<br />\n<br />\n我相信小弟行咗人生三份之一，冇錢冇女冇車冇樓冇運冇家底咗咁多年，上天一定會開返條路，我就係同個天賭梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以由今日起，小弟隨緣報倉，但唔會報本金同賺蝕 (eg. 連登仔個個都手揸成球以上，小弟報嚟盞俾人笑)。各位賤命嘅朋友，有興趣一齊同上帝賭返鋪嘅可以跟買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n揸金：<br />\n冚球爆，長升長有，但短期理應回調到 1350 附近<br />\n<br />\n揸銀：<br />\n同上，一樣長升長有，短站技術回調<br />\n<br />\n天然氣：<br />\n等金銀回調，同時賭技術，期貨睇吓升唔升得上 5-6 蚊，期貨穿 2 蚊止蝕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/usguYvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FusguYvV.jpg&h=ba02ef10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0009710f448b2627c7debba28d0835a78358fff0","tid":1518871,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=8d31e902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></sp